        <span class="hw">

            <span class="elementNoteDictionarySave pointer"><span class="icon-disk"></span> Zapisz</span>
            <span class="elementNoteDictionaryEditHide pointer">Anuluj</span>
                        <span class="placeForLoaderImage"></span> <a href="#" class="helpTooltip" onclick="return false;" title="W tym polu możesz dodać notatkę, która będzie pojawiać się podczas powtórek w polu z pytaniem. Notatki są przydatne, jeżeli jakieś słowo myli Ci się z innymi." tabindex="-1"><span class="icon-message-info"></span></a>             <span class="dikiNoteLanguageKeyboard">
                        </span>
          </span>
        </span>
      </span>
    </span>
          </p>

          <ul class="sentencesul">
      <li>Subtlety has never been one of your strong points.<span class="recordingsAndTranscriptions"><span class="en-US hasRecording" title="American English"><span class="audioIcon icon-sound dontprint soundOnClick" tabindex="-1" data-audio-url="/images-common/en-ame/mp3/subtlety_has_never_been_one_of_your_strong_points.mp3"></span></span></span><span class="exampleSentencesRecording_1" data-sentenceRecordingUrl="/images-common/en-ame/mp3/subtlety_has_never_been_one_of_your_strong_points.mp3"></span><span class="repetitionAddOrRemoveLinkWrapper">    <a class="repetitionAddOrRemoveIconAnchor noUnderline" href="#" onclick="RepetitionItemManager.addOrRemoveElement(this,
       5104694,
       true);
            return false;">
